snippet.title: Spider Waifu ❤️ - Monster Girl Island
snippet.description:
That's how I met your mother...
MGI Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLx_GoXwrHSqF2aruxK23cvF9Inue2BTGz
Game is available on the Monster Girl Island Patreon page~

Edited, no commentary (for more immersion) gameplay I recorded for entertainment purposes and to brighten our days, scenes which we can revisit without playing the whole game again~
